WEBVTT

00:03:59.250 --> 00:04:01.000
Geordie izdeluje...

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:03.760
(žvenket)

00:04:03.760 --> 00:04:06.170
(brnenje)

00:04:06.170 --> 00:04:08.920
Nedavno smo jih nesli na RISD

00:04:08.920 --> 00:04:12.120
in jih dali oblikovalcem
čisto brez izkušenj v konstruiranju -

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:15.570
samo karton, les in papir -
in jim rekli: "No, ustvarite nekaj!"

00:04:16.530 --> 00:04:18.060
Tu je primer enega projekta:

00:04:18.060 --> 00:04:20.960
Top, ki strelja konfete
in se aktivira ob zaznavi giba.

00:04:20.960 --> 00:04:22.670
(smeh)

00:04:22.670 --> 00:04:25.250
Ampak to je moj najljubši izdelek!

00:04:26.210 --> 00:04:29.000
Ta je jastog, narejen iz plastelina,